description: We're creating a world where sending digital currency is as easy as having a conversation with a friend. By using TeleX AI one can trade and invest faster, safer and with a more simplified and convenient user experience. All one has to do is open a chat with TeleX AI and enjoy wallet and exchange functionalities through an instant-messaging application interface. Telex (TLX) is an ERC20 token that is used to pay fees for the services offered by TeleX AI.
name: Telex
